para_trans: Regarding sanction of Sub-Centre at Mauje Bhandgaon Taluka, Paranda, District Dharashiv.
Government Decision No: Sub-Collections-2023 / P.No.361 / Health-4

Letter from Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries), Mumbai, No: ASSE / Room-7A / T-8 / Bhandgaon / Sub-Centre / Establishment / Dharashiv / 7618-29/2023, dated 13.11.2023.

Preamble: - The matter of sanctioning a sub-centre at Mauje Bhandgaon Taluka Paranda, District Dharashiv was under consideration of the Government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Government Decision: - The Government is approving the sanction of a Sub-Centre at Mauje Bhandgaon Taluka Paranda, District Dharashiv.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
